data.description: The seller is allowing the buyers the opportunity to do a 2.5%, qualifying assumption on their VA loan. This could save the buyers hundreds of dollars each month. Call agent for details. This like new Meritage home has foam insulation and a gas stove for energy efficiency. It has a rare option for a second living area. The room at the front of the home has barn doors and can be used as a large study, a send living area or a multi use bonus room. The home has carpet in the bedrooms. The rest is beautiful, low maintenance tile flooring. The spacious master bedroom has a bay window that faces the back yard. The master bath has a large walk in shower and garden tub. It also has two separate vanities with lots of counter space. The back has a large covered patio that overlooks a lush green backyard. The property has a smart home system installed by the builder and a sprinkler system in front and back.
